Identification?

1:05:29.667 --> 1:05:31.792
Vessel unknown,

1:05:29.667 --> 1:05:31.792
configuration unknown, sir.

1:05:41.041 --> 1:05:42.917
Hail it.

1:05:42.959 --> 1:05:46.542
We've been trying, sir--

